Fun¶

fight¶

Start a fight with another user.

`{prefix}fight @user2#2322 - Initiates a fight with @user2#2322
{prefix}fight @Snowplow#5196 670 - Initiates a fight with @Snowplow#5196 with a wager of 670xp`
